      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WEBLEC MAX (2) steps out for the first time at this track. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 2.75 lengths (34.65) at Sandown. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. JAFFA'S MONELLI (1) was sent out long odds last time but charged out of the boxes with a strong early sectional and went on to clock 22.53 in a 2.5 lengths win at this track over 400m. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Significant danger. BLAME HER (5) showed strong pace early from the inside rail and stuck on well despite missing the frame, finishing fifth over 488m this track in 27.85. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from three starts. Cannot be taken lightly. RHYTHMIC MOMENT (7) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
